ActNunavut Act
SubjectTransfer to the Commissioner of Nunavut (approximately 234 square metres)
PrecisOrder transfering to the COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT, in perpetuity, the administration and control of two surveyed parcels of land comprising the beds of bodies of water within two streams (approximatively 234 square metres), within the municipal boundaries of the hamlet of Pangnirtung.
